User Story

User can sign up with a class within a school that has an account with the site.
--School has many students. Student belongs to a school.

Once logged in, students can see class leader board to track their progress.

Students can click on a picture of a camera to request access to their camera and scan a QR code.

They will be redirected to a page that requests a code to be entered. One time use code is inside the box to prevent abuse.

The next time they open the app, they can simply enter another code without scanning again.

Their donation is recorded and they are rewarded with a link to ACT question or reading passage.

If they try to scan twice, there will be an error message to inform them that the code has already been used.



